<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1336931-are-there-rape-scenes-in-this-book-if-so">Are there rape scenes in this book? If so, are they graphic? Please help.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1336931'><a id="like_count_community_question_1336931" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1336931?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">52 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F35959740-circe">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1336931-are-there-rape-scenes-in-this-book-if-so">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1336931-are-there-rape-scenes-in-this-book-if-so">See all 30 answers</a>
</li>
